{"tid":2514870,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"放工見到前面上TG打手Group。。。","createTime":"2021-05-03T13:56:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T14:18:02.000Z","uid":71568,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4f43329a47ccf66b5bb9e2fcc5871ea73360be1e","tid":2514870,"uid":71568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:56:11.000Z","msg":"啱先放工搭車見到前面個男人上TG<br />\n唔小心望到佢成個group淨係得連登post既 share link，冇其他野<br />\n<br />\n咁我好奇就再認真睇<br />\n發現個谷名係叫&ldquo;打手XX&rdquo;  <br />\n(XX係我睇唔清楚)<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住個男人share完佢個post，就㩒入佢share出黎個post繼續上<br />\n<br />\n成程巴士見到佢時不時就share post，再comment，睇落似係提admin結數<br />\n<br />\n其實宜家唔難睇得出連登好多pr打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過撞到正一正好難唔令人懷疑到底自己上連登係睇緊d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"979ba234b4eec6626f4e9f8d8ef55b9388baa598","tid":2514870,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:56:54.000Z","msg":"我黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78d8ab2900742eae9e007b1f0c522184104d860","tid":2514870,"uid":71568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:57:28.000Z","msg":"然後我第一時間諗起viutv<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc183b3546584e281cf7b234b3f9d73b75213e6","tid":2514870,"uid":71568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"979ba234b4eec6626f4e9f8d8ef55b9388baa598","tid":2514870,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:56:54.000Z","msg":"我黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"好唔好賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc1679ab0dd5d113279ae0da179